name: Trang An Eco Tour from Hanoi
description: Spend full day to visit Trang An Eco Complex. Trang An Eco-Tourism complex is a home of 600 kinds of flora and over 200 kinds of fauna that many of them in the Red book of Vietnam. It is also a gathering of 31 valleys, 48 cross-water caves and we will visit up to 9 of them depend on the level of water
